divs: Sighting DetailsI was walking home at about 10pm and just looked up and there it was, a really big and bright star, but there were no other stars because of thick cloud cover. Then, it just took off flying to the north and it was simply gone. It looked like a super bright white baseball being thrown fast and high in the sky. I had no real feelings about seeing this thing other than I wished someone else could have seen it with me. If it is one of our secret aircrafts, we have some really cool stuff!
